#: includes/abilities/acf.php:64
msgid "List ACF field groups"
msgstr ""

#: includes/abilities/acf.php:65
msgid "Lists the ACF field groups and the fields inside each (key, label, and type) for discovery. It returns structure only, never stored values. Requires the edit-posts capability."
msgstr ""

