msgid "Update post SEO (All in One SEO)"
msgstr ""

#: includes/abilities/aioseo.php:74
msgid "Writes a post's SEO fields through All in One SEO's own data store (not post meta). URL fields are sanitized as URLs. Requires edit access to that post."
msgstr ""

