#: includes/admin/disclosures.php:131
msgid "Creates a WooCommerce product from a name, plus optional type, status, description, prices, SKU, stock, categories, tags, images, and attributes. Requires the manage-WooCommerce capability."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/disclosures.php:135
msgid "Creates a global WooCommerce product attribute taxonomy from a name, plus optional slug, type, sort order, and public-archives flag. Requires the manage-WooCommerce capability."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/disclosures.php:136
msgid "Updates a global product attribute taxonomy by id, changing only the fields you send. Requires the manage-WooCommerce capability."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/disclosures.php:138
msgid "Creates a refund on a WooCommerce order by order id. Accepts an amount, optional reason, and optional line-item breakdown. The refund reason is returned verbatim and may contain customer-entered text; it is returned under the Integrations security disclaimer. Requires the manage-WooCommerce capability."
